### ── ONBOARDING FLOW ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Utiliser un numéro qui n'existe PAS encore en DB (ex: +22699000099)

### O-1. Déclencheur — nouvel utilisateur (message quelconque → étape 0)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22699000099",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.onb01",
    "text": { "body": "Bonjour" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### O-2. Étape 1 — saisie de la ville
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22699000099",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.onb02",
    "text": { "body": "Ouagadougou" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### O-3. Étape 2 — saisie du secteur (doit retourner des boutons interactifs)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22699000099",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.onb03",
    "text": { "body": "Finance" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### O-4. Étape 3 — sélection du contrat via button_reply (crée User + Profile en DB)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22699000099",
    "type": "interactive",
    "id": "wamid.onb04",
    "interactive": {
      "type": "button_reply",
      "button_reply": { "id": "contract_cdi", "title": "CDI" }
    }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### O-5. Interruption AIDE pendant l'onboarding (retourne menu + relance la question)
### Reset d'abord Redis pour tester : DEL session:+22699000088:state
### puis simuler jusqu'à l'étape ONBOARDING_SECTOR :
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22699000088",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.onb05",
    "text": { "body": "AIDE" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### ── COMMANDES CLASSIQUES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Vérification webhook Meta (GET)
GET http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=tumaa_verify_2026&hub.challenge=CHALLENGE_CODE_123

###

### 2. OFFRES — Nouvel utilisateur (crée User + PullEvent + fenêtre Redis)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.001",
    "text": { "body": "OFFRES" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 3. VOIR 1 — Utilisateur FREEMIUM (doit retourner message de conversion)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.002",
    "text": { "body": "VOIR 1" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 4. AIDE
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.003",
    "text": { "body": "aide" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 5. STOP
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.004",
    "text": { "body": "STOP" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 6. Commande inconnue — doit retourner message d'aide
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000002",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.005",
    "text": { "body": "bonjour ça va ?" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### ── FLOWS INTERACTIFS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 7. Tap bouton "S'abonner" (Freemium) → déclenche handlePremium + state PREMIUM_CHOICE
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "interactive",
    "id": "wamid.006",
    "interactive": {
      "type": "button_reply",
      "button_reply": {
        "id": "subscribe",
        "title": "🔓 S'abonner – 650 FCFA/mois"
      }
    }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 8. Répondre PAYER pendant PREMIUM_CHOICE — state doit être PREMIUM_CHOICE en Redis
### Prérequis : exécuter la requête 7 d'abord
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.007",
    "text": { "body": "PAYER" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 9. Tap bouton "Voir les suivantes" (pagination SUITE) → déclenche handleSuite
### Prérequis : exécuter la requête 2 (OFFRES) d'abord pour initialiser l'offset Redis
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "interactive",
    "id": "wamid.008",
    "interactive": {
      "type": "button_reply",
      "button_reply": {
        "id": "suite",
        "title": "▶️ Voir les suivantes"
      }
    }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### ── GUARD-RAILS REDIS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 10. PREMIUM — affiche les offres d'abonnement
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.009",
    "text": { "body": "PREMIUM" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 11. ESSAI — active la période d'essai 48h (Freemium uniquement, usage unique)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.010",
    "text": { "body": "ESSAI" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 12. PARRAINER — affiche le code de parrainage et les crédits accumulés
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.011",
    "text": { "body": "PARRAINER" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 13. STATS — affiche le nombre d'offres actives pour le profil utilisateur
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.012",
    "text": { "body": "STATS" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 14. PAUSE — met l'utilisateur en pause (status=PAUSED)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.013",
    "text": { "body": "PAUSE" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### 15. MODIFIER — démarre le flow de modification du profil
POST http://localhost:3000/webhook/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [{"changes": [{"value": {"messages": [{
    "from": "+22670000001",
    "type": "text",
    "id": "wamid.014",
    "text": { "body": "MODIFIER" }
  }]}}]}]
}

###

### ── VÉRIFICATION REDIS (à exécuter dans redis-cli) ────────────────────────────
### Après requête 2 (OFFRES) :
###   GET user:+22670000001:window       → doit retourner "1"
###   GET session:+22670000001:offset    → doit retourner "5"
###
### Après requête 7 (subscribe button) :
###   GET session:+22670000001:state     → doit retourner {"step":"PREMIUM_CHOICE","data":{}}
###
### Après requête 5 (STOP) :
###   GET user:+22670000001:window       → doit retourner nil (TTL expiré ou supprimé)
###
### ── VÉRIFICATION DB (pgAdmin ou psql) ──────────────────────────────────────────
### SELECT * FROM "PullEvent" WHERE "userId" = (SELECT id FROM "User" WHERE phone='+22670000001');
### SELECT plan, status, "trialUsed" FROM "User" WHERE phone='+22670000001';
